## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of sources and the subjective nature of perceptions regarding racism. The complexity of racism as a social issue means that it is difficult to capture all nuances in a single report. Additionally, the reliance on online sources may not fully represent the breadth of academic research on the topic. Further research, including empirical studies and historical data analysis, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the changes in racism over time.

